  "text": "Anti-Müllerian hormone \" AMH was determined using an enzyme-linked immunoassay specific for human AMH (EIA AMH/MIS, Beckman Coulter Co., Marseilles, France), as previously validated by our group [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Intra-and inter-assay coefficients of variation (CV) were 10.5 and 9.4% for a serum AMH concentration of 700 pmol/l, and 11.1 and 12.8% for a serum AMH concentration of 7 pmol/l respectively.",
